think would be really great for an exhibition, who are ready for an exhibit=
ion, as well as who can pull off a giant outdoor mural, and they=E2=80=99re=
 paid a proposal fee. We don=E2=80=99t make public who the finalists are be=
cause we don=E2=80=99t want it to look like winners and losers out there. W=
e just want to celebrate the winners.<br/></td>
